{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_06_02",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 06 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、どうしてここにいるの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you two here…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 5.3696373304
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "だ、ダメだよ！　時間を無駄にしちゃ\n瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんは、ステージに立たないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No! You're wasting your time.\nRui-chan and Yu-chan need to be on stage!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 12.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "その言葉はそっくりそのまま返すわ、すみれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll return those words right back to you‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 15.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ステージに立たなければいけないのは、あなたも同じ\n沢山のファンが待っているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're the one who needs to be on stage too.\nA lot of fans are waiting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "そうや、すみれちゃんのおらんトリエルじゃ物足りんよ\nうちらも、ファンも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ TRINITYAiLE without Sumire-chan just isn't the same.\nBoth we and the fans",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 28.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "三人揃ってTRINITYAiLEなんやって\nず～っと言うてたやんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "have always said that\nTRINITYAiLE is the three of us together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 34.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……あの時、引き留められなくて後悔した\nごめんね、すみれの本心は分かってたはずなのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I regretted not stopping you then.\nI'm sorry‚ I should have understood your true feelings‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 43.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、私はもうトリエルには戻れない！\nお父さんが入院しちゃって、家を手伝わないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-But I can't go back to TRINITYAiLE!\nDad is hospitalized‚ I have to help out at home…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 54.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "すみれの事情は分かっているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand your situation‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、その上で、うちらは山形に来ることを決めたんや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ and even knowing that‚ we decided to come to Yamagata.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 61.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "……二人の気持ちは凄く嬉しい\nだけど、それだけじゃ問題は解決しないんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm really happy you feel that way.\nBut that alone won't solve the problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 69.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "今、お客さんがとっても少ないの。お金がないの\n二人が手伝ってくれても、どうにもならないことなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have very few customers now. We don't have money.\nEven if you two help‚ it won't change anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "家族みんなで頑張ってやっていくしか、方法が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The only way is for our family to work hard together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 85.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 88.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……朝倉社長に、言われたの\n私と優がここに来ても役に立たないって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Asakura-shachou told me\nthat Yu and I coming here wouldn't be helpful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "頭を冷やせ。君達が彼女の実家に居たところで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down. What good will it do",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一体なんの役に立つ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for you to be at her house?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……天動。自分のやるべきことを見失うな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Tendo. Don't lose sight of what you need to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "…………\n……嫌です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………\n…I refuse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……すみれは助けを求めている\nだから私達は、すみれを助けたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sumire is asking for help.\nThat's why we want to help her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "私達は、すみれを助けて\nかつ、三人での活動を継続します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We will help Sumire‚\nand continue our activities as three.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "すみれのいないTRINITYAiLEは\nありえません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE without Sumire\nis impossible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "――私達は、TRINITYAiLEは\n必ず三人揃って次のステージに立ってみせます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――We‚ TRINITYAiLE‚\nwill definitely stand on the next stage as three.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……天動",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Tendo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "私は、欲しいものは全部、手に入れます……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I will get everything I want…!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 140.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 140.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 146.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "る、瑠依ちゃん、そんなこと社長に言っちゃったの！？\nでも！　でも、私は……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Rui-chan‚ did you really say that to the president!?\nBut! But I…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 149.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 155.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "私は、助けてほしいだなんて一言も言ってないよ！\nこの酒造で私は……これから頑張るんだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never said I needed help!\nI'm… going to work hard here at the brewery from now on…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 160.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 162.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "こんなの無茶苦茶だよ。今からでもすぐ東京に戻って\n社長に謝って、なんとか許してもらって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is crazy. We need to go back to Tokyo right now‚\napologize to the president‚ and somehow get his forgiveness――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 170.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ、本当のことを教えて\nあなたが、どうしたいのかを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tell me the truth‚ Sumire.\nWhat you want to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 176.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "……トリエルを、続けたくはないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Don't you want to continue TRINITYAiLE?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 180.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 181.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "すみれは私達の中で一番幼いのに、物分かりが良過ぎる\n周りの人に遠慮して、自分の望みを引っ込めてしまう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire‚ you're the youngest of us‚ but you're too understanding.\nYou hold back your own desires because you're considerate of others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "そうやで。本当は……\nアイドル、辞めたくないんちゃうん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. The truth is…\nYou don't want to quit being an idol‚ do you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 197.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "それにお兄さんのことも、お家のことも諦めたくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And you don't want to give up on your brother or your family.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 201.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "せやったら、うちらにそう言ってくれたらええんよ\nもっと、東京のお姉ちゃん達に頼って？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then just tell us that.\nRely on your Tokyo sisters more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 209.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、そんなのわがまま過ぎる……\n私、言えないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-But that's too selfish…\nI can't say that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 217.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "私の事情につき合わせたら、トリエルの夢が……\nアイドルの頂点が、遠くに行っちゃうよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you get involved in my situation‚ TRINITYAiLE's dream…\nthe peak of being idols‚ it'll become distant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 226.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 230
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "そうやって、遠慮される方が私は嫌\nすみれ、これは私のわがままでもあるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hate it more when you hold back like that.\nSumire‚ this is also my selfishness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "――何があろうと\n私はあなたと、優と、アイドルの頂点に立つ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――No matter what happens‚\nI will reach the top of the idol world with you and Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 240.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
