      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、欲しいものが沢山あるなら\n全部自分のものにすればええ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah‚ if there are a lot of things you want‚\nyou should just make them all yours.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 246.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "女の子は、少～し欲張りなくらいがちょうどええんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just right for a girl to be a little greedy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 251.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
