      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "助けを必要としていないのなら、このまま帰るわ\n……すみれ。選んで、自分の意志で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you don't need our help‚ we'll leave.\n…Sumire. Choose‚ with your own will.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 272.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "……うっ、二人とも……ぐす……\nわ、私……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…U-Ugh‚ you two… Sob…\nI-I…!",
        "id": ""
      },
