      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "――そんな訳で、みなさんに\nうちらからの提案なんやけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――So‚ this is our\nproposition for you all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 311.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEの活動拠点を\n東京から山形に移します。一時的にですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're moving TRINITYAiLE's base of operations\nfrom Tokyo to Yamagata. Temporarily‚ at least.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 313.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 318.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smrmom001.m4a",
      "text": "なんですって！？\nどうして、そんなことまで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!?\nWhy would you go so far…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 320.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 323.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "すみれがTRINITYAiLEでの活動を継続して\nかつ、お店の売上を伸ばすためです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're doing this so that Sumire can continue her activities with TRINITYAiLE\nand also to increase your shop's sales.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 326.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 329.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "失礼ですが、調べさせてもらいました\nこちらのお酒の評価は悪くない、どころか上々です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ but I did some research.\nThe reviews for your sake are not bad‚ in fact‚ they're excellent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 333.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "売上が減ったのは、地域の過疎化によるところが\n一番の原因でしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The decline in sales\nis most likely due to depopulation in the area.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 341.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 342.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "ほんなら、よそから買いに来ていただきましょう\nうちらがマスコットになりますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ let's have people from other areas come to buy your sake.\nWe'll be your mascots.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 346.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 349.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "地元の商工会にも相談しましょう\n大規模な物販やステージも出来るかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's also talk to the local chamber of commerce.\nWe might be able to hold large-scale merchandise sales and stage performances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 352.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 355.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "お店の売上が伸びれば、お兄さんの留学資金も出せるし\n人も雇えて、すみれちゃんもアイドルを続けられます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If your shop's sales increase‚ you can afford your brother's study abroad‚\nhire more people‚ and Sumire-chan can continue being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 360.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 364.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "商工会とのやり取りやら、イベント準備やら大変やけど\n悪い話ではないと思いますが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It'll be a lot of work dealing with the chamber of commerce and preparing for events‚\nbut I don't think it's a bad idea…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 369.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smrbro001.m4a",
      "text": "いや、しかし、みなさんにご迷惑は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ but it'll be too much trouble for you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 372.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 377
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "お願い、お兄ちゃん。私、挑戦したい\n……私とお兄ちゃん、両方の夢を叶えるために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ big brother. I want to try this.\n…To achieve both my and your dream.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 383.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smrbro002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 387.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 389.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui024.m4a",
      "text": "お兄さん、失礼を承知で一言だけ\n言わせて頂けますか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Brother‚ I know this is presumptuous‚ but\nmay I say something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 393.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 395.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui025.m4a",
      "text": "夢は与えられるものでも\nましてや諦めたりするものでもありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Dreams are not something that are given‚\nnor are they something to be abandoned.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 397.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 406.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-rui026.m4a",
      "text": "自らの意志と行動で掴み取るものだと、私は思います\n私達に協力していただけないでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe they are something to be seized with one's own will and actions.\nWould you please cooperate with us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 406.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_02-smrbro003.m4a",
      "text": "…………分かりました\nよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………I understand.\nPlease take care of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 414.5,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
